402
00:22:10,500 --> 00:22:12,458
Where? Where?

403
00:22:12,541 --> 00:22:13,416
Uh--

404
00:22:17,333 --> 00:22:19,666
[FAVARO]
What the hell?

405
00:23:55,916 --> 00:23:57,166
[FAVARO]
Hey, Kaisar, know what's bad?

406
00:23:57,250 --> 00:23:58,416
[KAISAR]
What's bad?

407
00:23:58,500 --> 00:23:59,541
[FAVARO] I've gotta read
the next episode title

408
00:23:59,625 --> 00:24:00,625
and I don't think
there's enough time!

409
00:24:00,708 --> 00:24:01,791
[KAISAR]
Well, you're wasting time, now!

410
00:24:01,875 --> 00:24:03,083
[FAVARO]
Right!

411
00:24:03,166 --> 00:24:04,708
Rage of Bahamut: Genesis:
Escape From Livian!

412
00:24:04,791 --> 00:24:05,916
[KAISAR]
That wasn't hard at all.

